7754", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974817_1895786647291087_2489373001132714866_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lLGmuUYCBNcQ7kNvgGz5p15&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYApcDMWvtpRr7Q98tDrr_sTeA927RzCkE079OgM-Mt9Wg&oe=67307F91"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "HeroHiddenRealmsTitleCoverArt.png", "id": "3763628287026264", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974558_3763628290359597_6941369554397762485_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6K-SJeUZY2AQ7kNvgE8JQMV&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCVF2M3-zaR72XJMLSi6U4DJ6-chBHzKf5T1Lee-Q1CqA&oe=6730B28A"}, "display_name": "Dungeon of Nekros", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This is a one level demo for the upcoming full game. \n\nYou're alive again...but only for an hour! Temporarily resurrected from the dead, you find yourself in a musty old crypt, buried deep in the bowels of a dark & mysterious dungeon. Your only chance at becoming permanently alive again is to embark on a quest to retrieve the Necronomicon - a terrible & forbidden book desired by the one who resurrected you - Nekros the Necromancer. Discover treasure, fight monsters, & solve the mysteries of the Dungeon of Nekros in this amazing RPG by Hidden Realms.", "short_description": "You're alive again...but only for an hour! Temporarily resurrected from the dead, you find yourself in a musty old crypt, buried deep in the bowels of a dark & mysterious dungeon. Your only chance at becoming permanently alive again is to embark on a quest to retrieve the Necronomicon - a terrible & forbidden book desired by the one who resurrected you - Nekros the Necromancer. Discover treasure, fight monsters, & solve the mysteries of the Dungeon of Nekros in this amazing RPG by Hidden Realms."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://hiddenrealmsvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_ser